DAIA XSLT client
================

This module provides an XSLT stylesheet to convert DAIA/XML to HTML.
DAIA/XML is an XML serialization of Document Availability Information
(DAIA) as specified at L<http://purl.org/NET/DAIA>.

INSTALLATION

In order to use the DAIA client just copy all files or at least the 
following files into a directory:

- daia.xsl         - the core script
- xmlverbatim.xsl  - needed by daia.xsl
- daia.css         - CSS stylesheet
- icons/*          - icons (refered to in daia.css)

